<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en-us">
  <head>
    {% include "./head.njk" %}
  </head>
  <body>
    {% include "./header.njk" %}

    <!-- Main section-->
    <div id="main-section" class="container px-4">
      <nav aria-label="breadcrumb">
        <ol class="breadcrumb">
          <li class="breadcrumb-item"><a href="index.html">Home</a></li>
          <li class="breadcrumb-item active">{{title | safe}}</li>
        </ol>
      </nav>
      <main class="row gx-4 justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-lg-8">
          {% block title %}
          <h1>{{title}}</h1>
          {% endblock %}
          <div id="about">

          <h2>Contributors</h2>
          <ul>
            <li>Jon Gunderson, <a href="https://openweba11y.com">Open Web Accessibility Services</a></li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Previous Contributors</h2>

          <ul>
            <li>Nicholas Hoyt, University of Illinois (retired)</li>
            <li>Prasanna Bale, University of Illinois</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>Mission</h2>

          <ul>
            <li>To support the understanding and use of the following W3C specializations:
              <ul>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/wai-aria-1.2/">Accessible Rich Internet Application (ARIA) 1.2 Specification</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/html-aria/">Accessible Name and Description Computation 1.1</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/accname/">ARIA in HTML Specification</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG20/">Web content Accessibility Guidelines 2.0</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG21/">Web content Accessibility Guidelines 2.1</a></li>
                <li><a href="https://www.w3.org/TR/WCAG22/">Web content Accessibility Guidelines 2.2</a></li>
              </ul>
            </li>
            <li>Open Source for anyone to freely use in their own projects.</li>
            <li>Support the best practices for implementing accessible online resources.</li>
          </ul>

          <h2>History</h2>

          <p>The Evaluation library was originally developed as part of the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/OpenAjax_Alliance">OpenAjax Alliance</a>, when the OpenAjax Alliance ceased operations the accessibility evaluation library was rebranded to the <a href="https://github.com/opena11y/">OpenA11y GitHub organization</a>.

          <p><a href="https://github.com/opena11y/evaluation-library/blob/main/release-notes.md">View the release notes for the evaluation library.</a></p>

        </div>
      </main>
    </nav>
    {% include "./footer.njk" %}
    {% include "./scripts.njk" %}

  </body>
</html>
